%N A393320 Number of partitions p of n such that (maximal multiplicity of the parts of p) <= 2 * (minimal part of p).
%F A393320 G.f.: Sum_{j>=1} q^j*(1-q^(2*j^2))/(1-q^j) * Product_{k>=j+1} (1-q^((2*j+1)*k))/(1-q^k).
%e A393320 a(8) counts these 14 partitions: 8, 71, 62, 611, 53, 521, 44, 431, 422, 4211, 332, 3311, 3221, 2222.
%o A393320 (PARI) my(N=60, q='q+O('q^N)); Vec(sum(j=1, N, q^j*(1-q^(2*j^2))/(1-q^j)*prod(k=j+1, N, (1-q^((2*j+1)*k))/(1-q^k))))
